# ğŸŒ Routing: Directing Packets Across Networks

### ğŸ” What is Routing?

**Routing** à¦¹à¦²à§‹ network process à¦¯à¦¾à¦° à¦®à¦¾à¦§à§à¦¯à¦®à§‡ **data packets** à¦¸à¦ à¦¿à¦• **destination network** à¦ à¦ªà¦¾à¦ à¦¾à¦¨à§‹ à¦¹à§Ÿà¥¤

