* Optimizes path and reduces congestion
* Enables Internet communication

---

### âš™ï¸ How Routing Works

1. **Packet Creation:** Source device à¦¬à¦¾à¦¨à¦¾à§Ÿ packet with **destination IP**
2. **Routing Table Lookup:** Router à¦¦à§‡à¦–à§‡ à¦•à§‹à¦¨ interface à¦¬à¦¾ next hop à¦¦à¦¿à§Ÿà§‡ packet à¦ªà¦¾à¦ à¦¾à¦¨à§‹ à¦¹à¦¬à§‡
