4. **Repeat:** à¦ªà§à¦°à¦¤à¦¿à¦Ÿà¦¿ intermediate router à¦à¦•à¦‡ process à¦•à¦°à§‡ until destination

---

### ğŸ“Œ Types of Routing

| Type                     | Description                                           | Example            |
| ------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------------- | ------------------ |
